<i>noun</i>: 평탄 [평탄], 평온 [평온], 태연 [태연], 침착 [침착] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>평탄 [평탄]</dt><br>
<dd>1. evenness; flatness</dd><br>
<dd>바닥이 고르고 넓음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of a floor being even and spacious.</dd><br>
<dd>2. calmness; peace of mind</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 편하고 조용함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of one's mind being comfortable and quiet.</dd><br>
<dd>3. smoothness; favorableness</dd><br>
<dd>일이 미리 생각한 대로 잘되어 나감.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of a project, etc., being in smooth progress, as planned.</dd><br>
<dt>평온 [평온]</dt><br>
<dd>calmness; quietness; serenity</dd><br>
<dd>걱정이나 탈이 없고 조용함.</dd><br>
<dd>A quiet state without any worries or troubles.</dd><br>
<dt>태연 [태연]</dt><br>
<dd>calmness; composure; self-possession</dd><br>
<dd>당연히 머뭇거리거나 두려워할 상황에서 태도나 얼굴빛이 아무렇지도 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of showing no difference in attitude or complexion, in a situation in which one is expected to hesitate or be scared.</dd><br>
<dt>침착 [침착]</dt><br>
<dd>calmness; coolness; composure</dd><br>
<dd>쉽게 흥분하지 않고 행동이 조심스럽고 차분함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of acting carefully and calmly, not being excited easily.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>